metadata.name: The ephemerality
metadata.description:
//CIRCLE FORM//

The environment of our world is built on the attractor of constant events that occur according to the laws in order to continue the struggle against unreality, to continue the struggle for truth, as a constant cyclical renewal of the universe. But the natural struggle should not cross the line of the artificially created struggle, which led to the problems of senseless victims in each of the worlds.
